<div id="middlebit" class="row">
    <p><mark>One True Faith</mark> is a passion project to collect info about cool or obscure indie tape 
    releases. There is no strict criteia, Just got to be tape and dope.
    <br><br>If <mark>you</mark> know of a dope indie tape release and want it added, 
    dm me on twitter <a href="https://x.com/Jack_Clark_Ross">[@Jack_Clark_Ross]</a>
